  "texts": [
    "This dataset was partitioned into mutually exclusive training (75%), validation (10%), and test (15%) sets, ensuring that each patient could only belong to one of these subsets, for the training and evaluation of DeepCoro's Algorithm 6.",
    "Dataset B consists of 1926 videos of the LCA and RCA from 1628 patients, randomly selected from the MHI database.",
    "This selection occurred after the initial application of Algorithms 1-3.",
    "The purpose of this specific curation was to ensure that the dataset included only LCAs and RCAs with stenoses, facilitating the testing of our pipeline's performance against a human-annotated dataset.",
    "All videos were simultaneously annotated by two cardiologists (interface shown in Supplementary Fig. 2) with over 10 years of experience in reading CAG videos to describe stenosis percentage (1926 labels), correctness of the artery segment registration (Algorithm 3; 1926 labels), identification of the coronary artery segment with a stenosis (1926 labels) and presence of PCI in the video (i.e."
  ]
